\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 [Case reading | Mayor\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s office, City Hall: 11 PM]}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 It was a cold windy day as a storm was beginning to brew after a long week of summer head. A silhouette looms behind the mayor\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s desk revealing a pale body of the once beloved mayor. That night, the curtains were left open allowing the enthusiastic rain to soak the mayor on the spot. His body discovered by his daughter Kale who has reached out to him to return for dinner. No evidence was discovered in the scene of the crime.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 [Scene reveals to be the police station]}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 CHIEF}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 What kind of bastard would do such a thing? }
