\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 CHIEF}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Yes, Madam?}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 MADAM HOPPIN}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The person who\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s done this has disrupted the balance of not only this town but the lives of this family. My husband was a peaceful man who saw potential in this town and cared for its townsfolk as if they were his own family.  I want you to find whoever did this and see that they receive the same punishment by any means necessary.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 CHIEF}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Understood.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 [Chief leaves city hall to return to the police station]}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 CHIEF}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8230\'85Unbelievable. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 First people in town have gone missing and now the mayor?!}
