\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The chief does not trust me with a case this big, so they are requesting help from you it seems.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 VERMONT}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I see, I am sorry but I can\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t take the case. I am retired and have been out of the field for years. I came to this town to finally find peace. Please tell your Chief that I respectfully decline. This is none of my business and I do not want any more stress in my life.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 [PLAYER]}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Please ma\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92am. This is not just a regular case; the livelihood of the whole town is at stake. }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
