\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 MADAM HOPPIN}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The townsfolk are feeling restless after the assassination of my husband. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 And I fear things are getting worse.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 [MADAM HOPPIN gives more reports of missing people in town]}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1                  }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 MADAM HOPPIN}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 People are going Missing Vermont and the police\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8230\'85they will not disclose this to the public but even they are fearful of their own lives to do anything about it. }
