\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 VERMONT}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 This has nothing to do with me.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 MADAM HOPPIN}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 That may be so, but this is not just a regular late night bar quarrel. This is real, Vermont. If the police will not do anything, I can only trust a true professional to manage this case. You came to this town to finally have your freedom and I respect that but please, please help us Inspector Vermont.}
